HELP=$"
grimoire	none	 	all merged and indexed spells"

LONG=$"
While somewhat less than obvious 
the grimoire is the name of the catalog of available software.
The grimoire command lists all the available spells that from
installed grimoires that have been merged and indexed.
However, the grimoire command is usually only useful
when piped through grep, sed, or less.

Example:
augur grimoire | grep -i \"^sdl\""

param(){ :;}

run(){ show_grimoire; }
